`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Immortal_Rules
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

* Show maturity and responsibility in your words and actions at all times.
 * Do not compromise the integrity of your immortal by having any types of
interaction with your mortal alts. This includes ploading and transferring
equipment.
 * Try to keep punishments as regular as possible
 * Do not give gifts to mortals (unless it is earned, or a special occasion,
and at that make it reasonable)
 * Do not rename characters without a good reason (being that they have an
illegal name)
 * Do not interfere with PK
 * Immortals that do not attend to their duties without a valid explanation
will result in the removal of their immortal character
 * Do not carry on extensive conversations over public channels while
invis/incog
 * When punishing mortals, please write a penalty note to the immortal staff
and then a regular note to the mortal explaining reasons for the penalty
 * Respect fellow immortal staff and mortals
 * Please try and stay with the standard penalties
 * Use your best judgment
 * Always show respect towards mortals and immortals and they will show respect
towards you. Use your common sense and don't try to play God.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
